A\bar{x}\leq \bar{b}
S :=\{\sum \lambda_{i} x_{i} \}
\text{S is a convex space iff } \begin{cases} \sum \lambda_{i} = 1 \\  \lambda_{i} \in [0,1]\\ \lambda_{i} \geq 0 \\ \end{cases} 
S = \{x : Ax \leq b \}
Ax \geq b
n \in \mathbb{N}
n
S
x_1,x_2,\ldots,x_n
x_k \in S
k \in \{1,2,\ldots,n\}
n
\lambda_j
\displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{n} \lambda_j = 1
x = \displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{n} \lambda_j x_j \in S
x_j \in S
Ax_j \leq b
S
Ax = A \left( \displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{n} \lambda_j x_j \right) = \displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{n} A \left(\lambda_j x_j \right) = \displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{n} \lambda_j A x_j \leq \displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{n}\lambda_j b = \left(\displaystyle \sum_{j=1}^{n} \lambda_j \right) b = b
Ax \leq b.
